# PHP8.0 + PHPStorm + Xdebug



## 1. Installation

### （1）Install PHPStorm

DownLoad Llink : https://www.jetbrains.com/phpstorm/promo/?source=google&medium=cpc&campaign=14335686138&term=phpstorm&content=604147130387&gclid=CjwKCAjw586hBhBrEiwAQYEnHQ3ZosUYj98exUlpTtlGizssVKikg-j9wLOMLCrrbG0P4362c1fAfhoC6coQAvD_BwE

==Note== : if you are University Student, you can apply student account, 1 year for free

link :  https://www.jetbrains.com/community/education/#students/



### (2) Install Php 

Since I am using **MacOS** : 

The quickest way to install php on macOS is with homebrew:

1. install homebrew 

   link : https://brew.sh/

2. open Terminal , run : 

   ```
   brew install php
   ```

   ==Note== : if you want to install specific verison of php, run : 

   brew install php@with the version you are going to install , for example : brew install php@8.0

   ```
   brew install php@8.0   //it will install a specific php verison
   ```

3. check install succcessufully ?

   ```
   php -v
   ```

4. 刷新php连接, 如果你有多个版本的Php， 可以使用这个语句， 加上你的version

   ```
   brew link php@8.0
   ```

   ==Note :==  https://blog.csdn.net/qq_37200336/article/details/125584670?spm=1001.2101.3001.6650.5&utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7EBlogCommendFromBaidu%7ERate-5-125584670-blog-115815259.235%5Ev28%5Epc_relevant_default_base1&depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7EBlogCommendFromBaidu%7ERate-5-125584670-blog-115815259.235%5Ev28%5Epc_relevant_default_base1&utm_relevant_index=6

